org.vanilladb.core.remote.jdbc

Class JdbcMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vanilladb.core.remote.jdbc.ResultSetMetaDataAdapter
      • org.vanilladb.core.remote.jdbc.JdbcMetaData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResultSetMetaData, Wrapper

    public class JdbcMetaData
extends ResultSetMetaDataAdapter
    An adapter class that wraps RemoteMetaData. Its methods do nothing except transform RemoteExceptions into SQLExceptions.
